<section class="hero">
  <h1>Learn vocabulary that actually sticks — by solving crosswords built around the words you're learning.</h1>
  <p class="lede">Flashcards work, but they're a chore. Lexi runs real spaced
  repetition underneath dynamically generated crossword puzzles, so every
  review is a puzzle clue instead of a card flip — and every word shows up in
  a full sentence, in context, the way you'll actually meet it in the wild.</p>
  <p>
    <a class="btn btn-big" href="{{ site.appstore }}">Download free on the App&nbsp;Store</a>
  </p>
  <p class="muted">iPhone &amp; iPad · free · no account required</p>
</section>

